flowchart TD
    Start([Start Quick Sort]) --> Input[Input: Media List<br/>low index, high index]
    Input --> CheckBase{low < high?}

    CheckBase -->|No| End([End - Already Sorted])
    CheckBase -->|Yes| Partition[Call Partition Function<br/>Get pivot index]

    Partition --> PartStart[Partition Process:<br/>Choose pivot = arr high]
    PartStart --> InitI[Set i = low - 1]
    InitI --> LoopJ[Loop j from low to high-1]

    LoopJ --> CompareJ{arr j <= pivot?}
    CompareJ -->|No| NextJ[Continue to next j]
    CompareJ -->|Yes| IncrementI[Increment i]

    IncrementI --> SwapIJ[Swap arr i with arr j]
    SwapIJ --> NextJ

    NextJ --> CheckJLoop{More elements<br/>to check?}
    CheckJLoop -->|Yes| LoopJ
    CheckJLoop -->|No| FinalSwap[Swap arr i+1 with pivot]

    FinalSwap --> ReturnPivot[Return pivot index<br/>pivotIndex = i + 1]
    ReturnPivot --> RecurseLeft[Recursive Call:<br/>QuickSort left, low, pivotIndex-1]

    RecurseLeft --> RecurseRight[Recursive Call:<br/>QuickSort right, pivotIndex+1, high]
    RecurseRight --> End

